title: The Show (Part 2)
itunes:title: The Show (Part 2)
description: Following up from last week's show, Dave Garofalo, Mr Jonathan and Chuck Morrison talk about the all the news and events from this year's ICPPR in Las Vegas. Today the boys smoke the new Swagg Limitado 99', and the exclusive micro brand Canimao. It's time for the finer things in life... It's time for The Cigar Authority!
